  "detailed_description": "<h1>Roadmap</h1><p><strong>ABEYANCE</strong> is a living game and we plan to release regularly new content in the form of updates and DLCs. This is the <strong>roadmap</strong> of the upcoming updates:<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Version 1.0 (November 2022)</h2>Improving combat <strong>interface</strong>.<br>Improving game stability and <strong>performance</strong>.<br>Improving the <strong>balance</strong> of the game.<br>Implementing the music player.<br>Improving the user experience and the user interface.<br>Optimizing for 100% <strong>Steam Deck</strong> compatibility.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Version 1.1 (December 2022)</h2>Adding more <strong>variation</strong> to armors' look and qualities.<br>Adding more variation to weapons' looks and qualities.<br>Adding more variation to the NPCs' look.<br>Adding more variation to the environments.<br>Adding support for two hot-swap implants.<br>Implementing <strong>consumable</strong> items.<br>Keeping balancing the game. Adding different challenges and <strong>difficulty levels</strong>.<br>Adding support for at least two other <strong>languages</strong>.<br>Releasing the <strong>soundtrack</strong>.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >December 2022 / January 2023</h2>Release on <strong>XBOX</strong>.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Version 2.0 (Q1 2023)</h2><strong>Free DLC</strong> with new story content and gameplay mechanics.<br>Support for <strong>Steam Workshop</strong> and modding</p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1774200/extras/af270790fa93db3439a3c5704d60105d.poster.avif?t=1737490516\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1774200/extras/af270790fa93db3439a3c5704d60105d.webm?t=1737490516\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1774200/extras/af270790fa93db3439a3c5704d60105d.mp4?t=1737490516\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>In a scorched world devastated by a decades-long interstellar war, you, Ezra, have been recruited by the all-powerful Recovery Syndicate to salvage items from abandoned spaceships and military bases. With no memories, and cerebral implants threatening your autonomy, you go on missions, battle mutants and defense systems, and bring loot back to the Recovery Syndicate.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1774200/extras/aa79a5967efc17938f7d6e45371cf021.poster.avif?t=1737490516\" width=640 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1774200/extras/aa79a5967efc17938f7d6e45371cf021.webm?t=1737490516\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1774200/extras/aa79a5967efc17938f7d6e45371cf021.mp4?t=1737490516\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>That is, until you uncover clues about your past. Once the truth is revealed, you can’t go back. It's war against a powerful evil and your inner demons. Fight to regain your humanity or die trying.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1774200/extras/66013fd68c297c2342dc68c020fc36b7.poster.avif?t=1737490516\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1774200/extras/66013fd68c297c2342dc68c020fc36b7.webm?t=1737490516\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1774200/extras/66013fd68c297c2342dc68c020fc36b7.mp4?t=1737490516\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>This dark and dystopian, procedurally generated, dungeon crawler adventure game will immerse you in a hypnotic world as you fight for your freedom:<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Single-player roguelite gameplay<br></li><li>Frantic real-time dungeon exploration<br></li><li>Story-driven character development<br></li><li>Fast-paced tactical fighting<br></li><li>Randomly generated levels for endless fun<br></li><li>Play with a controller or with mouse and keyboard<br></li><li>Original soundtrack featuring indie artists</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1774200/extras/bbb0ef105f43fb19e78cabe1e0929196.poster.avif?t=1737490516\" width=614 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1774200/extras/bbb0ef105f43fb19e78cabe1e0929196.webm?t=1737490516\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1774200/extras/bbb0ef105f43fb19e78cabe1e0929196.mp4?t=1737490516\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1774200/extras/af270790fa93db3439a3c5704d60105d.poster.avif?t=1737490516\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1774200/extras/af270790fa93db3439a3c5704d60105d.webm?t=1737490516\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1774200/extras/af270790fa93db3439a3c5704d60105d.mp4?t=1737490516\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>In a scorched world devastated by a decades-long interstellar war, you, Ezra, have been recruited by the all-powerful Recovery Syndicate to salvage items from abandoned spaceships and military bases. With no memories, and cerebral implants threatening your autonomy, you go on missions, battle mutants and defense systems, and bring loot back to the Recovery Syndicate.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1774200/extras/aa79a5967efc17938f7d6e45371cf021.poster.avif?t=1737490516\" width=640 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1774200/extras/aa79a5967efc17938f7d6e45371cf021.webm?t=1737490516\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1774200/extras/aa79a5967efc17938f7d6e45371cf021.mp4?t=1737490516\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>That is, until you uncover clues about your past. Once the truth is revealed, you can’t go back. It's war against a powerful evil and your inner demons. Fight to regain your humanity or die trying.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_as